# Emeq Hub × Exact Online — pass-through + accounting-sync smoke-tests
#
# Werkt met de VS Code "REST Client"- of JetBrains HTTP-client-extensie.
# Dit test de HÚB-endpoints (/v1/*), niet de SDK direct.
#
# Setup:
#  - PAT op de Consumer "Naschool" met abilities exact:read + exact:write.
#  - X-Account-Id = Account.external_id ("school1"), gescoped op die Consumer.
#  - Connection 1 levert de division (administratie_id = 4471372).
#  - Mapping (connection.metadata.accounting_mapping): tarief 21 → VATCode "3";
#    category "omzet"/"kosten" → GLAccount (onbekend → _default); relaties
#    HUB-TEST-KLANT → klant-GUID, HUB-TEST-LEVERANCIER → leverancier-GUID;
#    dagboeken sales=80 / purchase=70 / general=90.
#
# LET OP:
#  - De TOKEN is een secret + leeft alleen lokaal (packages/ is gitignored).
#    Na `migrate:fresh` opnieuw minten:
#    php artisan tinker --execute '$c=App\Models\Account::find(1)->consumer; echo $c->createToken("exact-passthrough-demo",["exact:read","exact:write"])->plainTextToken;'
#  - Idempotency-Key is verplicht op /v1/accounting/documents. {{$uuid}} (VS Code
#    REST Client: {{$guid}}); varieer per logisch document — dezelfde sleutel = replay.

@baseUrl = http://hub.emeq.test:8092
@token = 1|wrPgnECgeICPLsrW2GfOu0L7jguKSEUn80Hjlwl10d8a5a79
@accountId = school1
# Minimale geldige PDF (base64) — hergebruikt als bijlage.
@pdfBase64 = JVBERi0xLjEKMSAwIG9iajw8L1R5cGUvQ2F0YWxvZy9QYWdlcyAyIDAgUj4+ZW5kb2JqCjIgMCBvYmo8PC9UeXBlL1BhZ2VzL0tpZHNbMyAwIFJdL0NvdW50IDE+PmVuZG9iagozIDAgb2JqPDwvVHlwZS9QYWdlL1BhcmVudCAyIDAgUi9NZWRpYUJveFswIDAgMjAwIDIwMF0+PmVuZG9iagp0cmFpbGVyPDwvUm9vdCAxIDAgUj4+CiUlRU9GCg==

### 1. OAuth-init — maakt pending Connection + geeft de Exact authorize-URL terug
#    (alternatief op de admin-connect; open de redirect_url in je browser)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/oauth/exact/init
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "account_external_id": "{{accountId}}"
}

### 2. Pass-through GET — 1 CRM-relatie (division-scoped, read-only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/exact/crm/Accounts?$top=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Account-Id: {{accountId}}

### 3. Pass-through GET — divisions die deze koppeling ziet
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/exact/system/Divisions?$top=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Account-Id: {{accountId}}

### 4. Pass-through GET — alleen ID + Name (OData $select), netter resultaat
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/exact/crm/Accounts?$top=3&$select=ID,Name,Status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Account-Id: {{accountId}}

### --- Named read-resources (eigen Scramble-groep; voeden de boekhoud-mapping-UI) ---
#    Elk endpoint mapt 1-op-1 op één gedocumenteerde Exact OData-endpoint en logt
#    de geraakte path in pass_through_calls, net als de generieke pass-through.

### 5a. GL Accounts → Exact financial/GLAccounts
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/exact/gl-accounts?$top=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Account-Id: {{accountId}}

### 5b. VAT Codes → Exact vat/VATCodes (tarief→VATCode-referentie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/exact/vat-codes?$top=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Account-Id: {{accountId}}

### 5c. Relations → Exact crm/Accounts (relatie→GUID-referentie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/exact/relations?$top=5&$select=ID,Name,Code
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Account-Id: {{accountId}}

### 5d. Journals → Exact financial/Journals (doc-type→dagboek-referentie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/exact/journals?$top=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Account-Id: {{accountId}}

# =====================================================================
#  ACCOUNTING-SYNC — v1-scenario's (consumer → Exact: verkoop + inkoop)
# =====================================================================
#  De scenario-naam staat in "number" → zichtbaar als Description in Exact
#  (Verkoop/Inkoop > Openstaande posten) en als Document-Subject.
#  Bijlage = canonical attachments[] (inline base64); de Hub doet ná de boeking
#  automatisch de 2-staps Document + DocumentAttachment, gekoppeld via
#  FinancialTransactionEntryID (boeking) + Account (relatie).
#
#  A = Verkoop (klant, debtor)  ·  B = Inkoop (leverancier, creditor)
#  C = ad-hoc income → SalesEntry, expense → PurchaseEntry — live sinds #12
#      (relatie + BTW + categorie; openstaande post later via bankreconciliatie).

### A1. Verkoopfactuur + factuur-PDF → SalesEntry + Document (Verkoop openstaand)  ⚠️ SCHRIJFT
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/accounting/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Account-Id: {{accountId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$uuid}}

{
  "type": "sales_invoice",
  "external_id": "A1-INV",
  "number": "A1 verkoop +bijlage",
  "issue_date": "2026-06-17",
  "party": { "role": "debtor", "name": "Hub Test Klant", "external_id": "HUB-TEST-KLANT" },
  "lines": [
    { "description": "Consultancy", "amount": 200, "tax_rate": 21, "category": "omzet" }
  ],
  "attachments": [
    { "filename": "A1-factuur.pdf", "mime_type": "application/pdf", "content": "{{pdfBase64}}" }
  ]
}

### A2. Verkoopfactuur ZÓNDER bijlage → SalesEntry, géén Document  ⚠️ SCHRIJFT
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/accounting/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Account-Id: {{accountId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$uuid}}

{
  "type": "sales_invoice",
  "external_id": "A2-INV",
  "number": "A2 verkoop (geen bijlage)",
  "issue_date": "2026-06-17",
  "party": { "role": "debtor", "name": "Hub Test Klant", "external_id": "HUB-TEST-KLANT" },
  "lines": [
    { "description": "Consultancy", "amount": 120, "tax_rate": 21, "category": "omzet" }
  ]
}

