### --- Foutpaden (verwachte 4xx) ---

### F1. Ontbrekende X-Account-Id → 400 missing_account_header
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/exact/crm/Accounts?$top=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### F2. Onbekend account → 404 account_not_found
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/exact/crm/Accounts?$top=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Account-Id: bestaat-niet

### F3. Niet-toegestane method (HEAD) → 405 method_not_allowed
HEAD {{baseUrl}}/v1/exact/crm/Accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Account-Id: {{accountId}}
